  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Re-Volt is an R/C car racing game from Acclaim, originally released in 1999.\nRe-Volt features great gameplay, realistic physics that still hold up to this day and bright and colorful visuals. It's a game aimed at people who just want to play a funky arcade racing game as well as for people who seek a more competitive challenge. It's meant for all ages and occasions: Play for yourself or in the local network with friends, or even online!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
